 ative wrap-up goes beyond recapping bills and votes. Together\, we’ll br
 eak down how power actually moves in the legislature\, who influences outc
 omes\, what happens behind the scenes\, and why pressure doesn’t stop wh
 en a session ends. Participants will learn how to apply ethical\, strategi
 c pressure on lawmakers\, understand the levers of accountability that exi
 st outside the Statehouse\, and identify concrete ways to keep elected off
 icials a
